{"tid":1199980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃英豪 總有一日你會為你做既嘢感到後悔","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:45:32.000Z","uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57fe23a0059e02ac368483d2dd15148524e9088b","tid":1199980,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"支持修例？激進者嚴重誇大條例後果？<br />\n條例只適用於嚴重罪犯？<br />\n你究竟識唔識法律 仲學人做律師？<br />\n咩叫嚴重？批評共產黨？打擊時弊？<br />\n咩叫嚴重都唔係你話事啦 你唔好係到派定心丸比班廢老啦<br />\n就係你哩啲人 收左錢就亂咁宣傳歪理 <br />\n就搵啲廢料老入坑 <br />\n到時香港會變成點 大家心照啦<br />\n到時邊個係支持修例既最大功臣 <br />\n係你啊 到時個個都指著你黎鬧啊 賣港賊"},{"pid":"3f2eaf60d0a49ef0209a2060395b2ebfa6429ed9","tid":1199980,"uid":38364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"［速投］十一號晚定十二號頭班車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199753</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩入去投個票，再唔出黎就真係太遲啦香港人"},{"pid":"3b757818d9c529aaae0edfaafbfd3ddca8f75751","tid":1199980,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"律師黃英豪被指拖欠8700萬元被海外公司入稟追討｜香港01｜社會新聞<br />\n<br />\n撲水呀人地"},{"pid":"d5e8a2de5738cf1ff8bd322ee0fdc39019b53038","tid":1199980,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/10/234528_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F234528_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png&h=0528dce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（文宣組）612icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n【大整合】11/6-12/6 資訊整合 「反送中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199978</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}